data.title: About Us
data.meta_description: WHKY TalkRadio broadcast on both 1290 AM with 50,000 watts and on 102.3 FM to fully cover The Greater Hickory Metro area. WHKY has local, live morning talk show
data.text:
WHKY Radio signed on June 10, 1940 and transmits on 1290 AM and 102.3 FM.

Format: News/Talk with emphasis on local news, sports and information.

Hours of Operation: 24 hours a day, 7 days a week

Power: AM 50,000 watts directional daytime, 1,000 watts directional nighttime. FM 250 watts

Transmitter Coordinates: AM: Longitude North 35°43’35.0″N , Latitude West 81°18’02.0″W | FM: 35° 39′ 28.50″ N Latitude 81° 24′ 23.30″ W Longitude (NAD 27)
